article:
List of the 'National Register of Historic Places listings in Manhattan above
110th Street'


This is intended to be a complete list of properties and districts listed on the
National Register of Historic Places above 110th Street in Manhattan. For
properties and districts in other parts of Manhattan and the other islands of
New York County, see National Register of Historic Places listings in New York
County, New York. The locations of National Register properties and districts
(at least for all showing latitude and longitude coordinates below) may be seen
in a Google map by clicking on "Map of all coordinates".


__NOTOC__
